- [ ] No breaking changes (or documented)
- [ ] Security review passed
- [ ] Documentation updated
```

## Fallback

If analysis is inconclusive:
- Flag for manual review with specific concerns
- Request additional context from PR author
- Escalate security-sensitive changes to security team
